additionalNotes:
The Primos Estate Selection Habano Criollo Rosado is handmade in Nicaragua. It is a medium-strength cigar that features a natural Nicaraguan Habano wrapper placed over a Honduran binder and a filler made up of tobaccos from Honduras, Nicaragua, and Peru.
